# 회의록 — <%= meeting_title %>

**일시**: <%= meeting_date %> <%= meeting_time %>
**장소**: <%= location || "(미기록)" %>
**참석**: <%= attendees.is_a?(Array) ? attendees.join(", ") : attendees %>
**작성자**: <%= recorder || teacher_name %>

<% if absent_members && !Array(absent_members).empty? %>
**불참**: <%= Array(absent_members).join(", ") %>
<% end %>

---

## 안건

<% (agenda || []).each_with_index do |item, i| %>
<%= i + 1 %>. <%= item %>
<% end %>

## 논의 내용

<%= discussion || "(작성 필요)" %>

## 결정 사항

<% (decisions || []).each do |d| %>
- <%= d %>
<% end %>

## 다음 회의

<%= next_meeting || "(미정)" %>

